.. -*- rst -**

Change Log
==========

Release 0.3.1 - (March 2, 2014)
-------------------------------
* Switch to PEP 440 version numbering.
* Include ez_setup.py.
* Assume optional config file is in standard XDG_CONFIG_HOME location.
* Access docutils programmatically when building man page.
* Include built man page in source package so docutils isn't needed for
  installation.

Release 0.03 - (January 08, 2013)
---------------------------------
* Add support for optional configuration file.

Release 0.02 - (April 11, 2012)
-------------------------------
* Add support for more browsers.
* Add man page.
* Use default icons.

Release 0.01 - (March 05, 2012)
-------------------------------
* First public release.
